text: ¬†@mainAc-px9we¬† it was a fan who had the retired member of Hololive JP gen 5 member Mano Aloe. Within the first couple of days of her debut she was punished for leaking her live2d model before debuting properly. On top of this punishment, there was a huge amount of haters giving her grief for fairly minor things and taking it to the point of calling her home phone and supposed ex boyfriends phone, and sending Aloe's VA a flood of death threats. She retired the day she was supposed to come back from her suspension due to not feeling mentally strong enough for the job. It hit both Gen5 and the fans pretty hard when it happened, but both groups won't let her be forgotten. She appears in Nene's twitter banner, some various bits of layout art for gen5, and a ton of fanart still shows her with the rest of the group.
